thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGmbmlwlWDkCHoWCaeSVNcw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bztzcj0xLjI7c3M9MS4yO3c9NjAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fnevec-img.zenfs.com%2Fprod%2Ftw_ec05-7%2F6c9d760c-86da-4382-95fc-34bc2b6154bd.jpg&h=25ce7f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放隻曱甴入去，塞住針口位，不停加壓減壓睇住隻曱甴掙扎至死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd7a5d507dafecfd8e984046e66f49b313db7c1","tid":23643,"uid":45077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/GmbmlwlWDkCHoWCaeSVNcw--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bztzcj0xLjI7c3M9MS4yO3c9NjAw/http://nevec-img.zenfs.com/prod/tw_ec05-7/6c9d760c-86da-4382-95fc-34bc2b6154bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGmbmlwlWDkCHoWCaeSVNcw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bztzcj0xLjI7c3M9MS4yO3c9NjAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fnevec-img.zenfs.com%2Fprod%2Ftw_ec05-7%2F6c9d760c-86da-4382-95fc-34bc2b6154bd.jpg&h=25ce7f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放隻曱甴入去，塞住針口位，不停加壓減壓睇住隻曱甴掙扎至死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bde5ef64a31a811437027667f874d6c08b91a67","tid":23643,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.big5.made-in-china.com/37f28j01qeyQdRhkrgbZ/电蚊拍.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.big5.made-in-china.com%2F37f28j01qeyQdRhkrgbZ%2F%E7%94%B5%E8%9A%8A%E6%8B%8D.jpg%20&h=5b5e1808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試過用呢隻對付過隻識飛嘅<br />\n因為呢啲電蚊拍嘅電力唔夠做瓜佢<br />\n所以隻嘢就一路畀個電網黐住<br />\n一路拍翼同出煙<br />\n最後電甩咗一條觸鬚<br />\n啲曱甴係靠嗰兩條觸鬚平衡嘅<br />\n所以到最後隻曱甴就喺個地下自轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3f83db51bf88a2b780676518ff082a07f307ef","tid":23643,"uid":38397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"人為變態"},{"pid":"40fd4be36a90825019ddea1dc2e521166c8bf57b","tid":23643,"uid":31077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"滾水 既方便又快捷"},{"pid":"06fedf56f52794a1854f1ae5dc501fcea512f1ec","tid":23643,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:52:24.000Z","msg":"碧麗珠/<br />\n洗衫個D噴劑<br />\n所有化學野都噴落去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f058d375246a305833ccf728f18ddae3334157d7","tid":23643,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖涼液加水，一野飛過去，即死，試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為曱甴既腹部有層野 (好似係油), 同番皂水撈埋會溶咗層野, 之後好似係因為冇咗果層野保護所以會死<br />\n冇記錯好似係10秒內死"},{"pid":"8b6681591ea5f3a7152d93ae8d1ed535a109649f","tid":23643,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://image.big5.made-in-china.com/37f28j01qeyQdRhkrgbZ/%E7%94%B5%E8%9A%8A%E6%8B%8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.big5.made-in-china.com%2F37f28j01qeyQdRhkrgbZ%2F%25E7%2594%25B5%25E8%259A%258A%25E6%258B%258D.jpg&h=78065371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試過用呢隻對付過隻識飛嘅<br />\n因為呢啲電蚊拍嘅電力唔夠做瓜佢<br />\n所以隻嘢就一路畀個電網黐住<br />\n一路拍翼同出煙<br />\n最後電甩咗一條觸鬚<br />\n啲曱甴係靠嗰兩條觸鬚平衡嘅<br />\n所以到最後隻曱甴就喺個地下自轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前睇過有條片話澳洲有人為咗應付啲曱甴發明咗部機, , 圓柱體既, 不過中間有兩塊鐵片壓住塊用豆壓成粒藥片型既野, 啲曱甴聞到果塊野既味就行過黎, 因為果部機有6千幾Watt所以一行入到會燒死。而本身塊藥片既野對曱甴黎講唔係好大陣味, 所以一開始係好小曱甴入黎,  但係燒焦咗既曱甴就好大陣味, 所以入黎既曱甴愈來愈多"},{"pid":"a7e9b92aadb427a8f4e5673bfb481215781f1d9a","tid":23643,"uid":17530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2q6AV8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2q6AV8.jpg&h=0600f756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用劍"},{"pid":"aa2a535e1b8a12412fc1c4ef672d695576046299","tid":23643,"uid":51058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/GmbmlwlWDkCHoWCaeSVNcw--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bztzcj0xLjI7c3M9MS4yO3c9NjAw/http://nevec-img.zenfs.com/prod/tw_ec05-7/6c9d760c-86da-4382-95fc-34bc2b6154bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGmbmlwlWDkCHoWCaeSVNcw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bztzcj0xLjI7c3M9MS4yO3c9NjAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fnevec-img.zenfs.com%2Fprod%2Ftw_ec05-7%2F6c9d760c-86da-4382-95fc-34bc2b6154bd.jpg&h=25ce7f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放隻曱甴入去，塞住針口位，不停加壓減壓睇住隻曱甴掙扎至死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}